hansi-font-family:仿宋;\">第二十条</span><span style=\"font-family:方正仿宋简体;font-size:16pt;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes;\">&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:方正仿宋简体;font-size:16pt;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋;\">驻村工作组和驻村干部年度考核成绩优秀的，由各县（市、区）通报表扬，年度考核不合格的通报批评，并将通报表扬或批评情况送达驻村干部派出部门（单位）和省、市（州）干部驻村帮扶工作考核组，作为干部培养、任用的重要依据和干部派出部门（单位）开展驻村帮扶工作的考核依据。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:28pt;text-indent:31.7pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:方正仿宋简体;font-size:16pt;mso-hansi-font-family:黑体;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:28pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family:方正黑体简体;font-size:16pt;mso-hansi-font-family:黑体;\">第七章<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes;\">&nbsp; </span></span>附则<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:28pt;text-indent:23.75pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;mso-char-indent-count:1.5;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:方正黑体简体;font-size:16pt;mso-hansi-font-family:黑体;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:28pt;text-indent:23.75pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;mso-char-indent-count:1.5;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:方正黑体简体;font-size:16pt;mso-hansi-font-family:黑体;\">第二十一条</span><span style=\"font-family:方正仿宋简体;font-size:16pt;mso-hansi-font-family:黑体;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes;\">&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:方正仿宋简体;letter-spacing:-0.6pt;font-size:16pt;mso-hansi-font-family:黑体;\">本办法由省干部驻村帮扶工作考核组负责解释</span><span style=\"font-family:方正仿宋简体;letter-spacing:-0.6pt;font-size:16pt;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋;\">。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: